{"tid":1217110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬，星期日預左少人更加要行出嚟","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:31:49.000Z","uid":87507,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8ae559916432e17c2ffd0c270102cb5f4caf3e","tid":1217110,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"民陣係on9，父親節叫人出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但正因為可能少人左，我哋更加要出嚟。因為只要比上一次少人左，柒婆就會以為民心已散，以為拖長時間我哋就會頹，就會放棄。我地以後有咩要求，政府同警察都唔會理，因為我地只係紙老虎。<br />\n<br />\n唔單止要行出嚟，更加要叫身邊嘅人同我地一齊行。我唔理你話你屋企人幾咁廢老都好，試一下，講下呢次唔出嚟對我地未來後代嘅危害。<br />\n<br />\n叫你朋友出嚟<br />\n叫你中學同學小學同學出嚟<br />\n叫你同事出嚟<br />\n叫埋你老細出嚟<br />\n叫你老豆老母出嚟<br />\n<br />\n今次唔衰得，衰左就係一世。6月16注定係一個難忘嘅父親節，我哋到時見"},{"pid":"ab190021920c4522827e1ec743fad45354450618","tid":1217110,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52d5ad5ca21d9e9de55c46f0cd37806354abe50e","tid":1217110,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"推呀 唔好等件事淡左呀 點對得住比人打爆 同捉左既義士？"},{"pid":"eab8fd6afbcb522ab9da10069c87aa2bb659dd1a","tid":1217110,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4afcdfe7167608a974dae53fd9d2560eb9ff4239","tid":1217110,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a8d49e8813735b15570b9725f091f2da41e952d","tid":1217110,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85ef7d4ceb825fbde6d99281c060c88b064f8c1b","tid":1217110,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"149f62790b8095055d5bdde1ecc2b232b36e087f","tid":1217110,"uid":71509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"話慶祝父親節都on9<br />\n<b